Product name: Vintage Floats Set of 5 Fishing Floats Glass Floats Japanese Beach Decor Nautical Coastal Decor
Description:
Vintage floats with nets add a fun coastal or nautical accent.  The set of 5 glass fishing floats were once used by Japanese fishermen on their squid nets.  The fishing floats measure about 2 to 2 1/2" in diameter (larger than a golf ball, smaller than a tennis ball).  Each float has a "button" or pontil of melted glass at the bottom.  Glass fishing floats are a fun decorative accent in your coastal beach house or lake house decor.
This listing is for one set of 5 authentic vintage glass fishing floats and I have 4 sets.  Please specify quantity of sets at check out.
The vintage floats are pretty sea glass greenish- bluish shades and all floats have assorted nets.  We will select an assortment for you, or  please state any preferences at checkout in the notes section.
Condition:  The glass is in vintage condition with some patina, bubbles and salt residue. The netting is mostly intact, with wear from bobbing in the ocean.  Some are marked Japan or with Japanese characters.

Product name: Baby Swing Chair 14" in Macrame. 1 Year Warranty. High Quality. Sustainable native wood bars. FairTrade. → 14 DAYS DELIVERY!
Description:
Baby Swing Chair in Macrame Knots. Cream color. Safety assembled. TOP QUALITY. 
Super nice outdoor for the upcoming sunny season!
Sitting area: 10'' x 10''
Designer: Hang A Hammock Collective
NOTE: the wood could be lighter or darker because we started to use a sustainable native wood (Madero Negro (Gliricidia sepium)) to avoid to cut precius wood from rain forest. The wood come from a plantation.
If this is not your preference, please write me.
SUPER GOOD NEWS:
- YOU CAN TRACK YOUR PARCEL WORLDWIDE
- NEW CUSHION WITH COTTON FIBERS INSIDE
DESCRIPTION
The Baby Swing Chair is made with care and love by Veronica, Yersi, Martin, David and Alonso; the cushion is made by Marlene, an expert seamstress and grandmother. All are permanent artisans of our team "Hang A Hammock Collective", regularly employed. 
We deliver Values not only items.
This is a new design of our baby swing chair for you.
The wood bars are made in Madero wood (Gliricidia sepium), a native nicaraguan tree. Madero it is not a species in danger of extinction, but is a fast-growing species, an environmentally friendly alternative. We are working to set a plantation of Madero wood to be able to certify the origin.
In this way we want to stand out from our competitors.
We made and we test each swing chair at our workshop based in Masaya. 
We follow a procedure in order to warranty a resistance up to 150 Kg (330 lbs), even if your baby will never be heavier than ~ 45 kg (~ 100 lbs)
Baby Swing Chair in macrame will makes your kid happy with a original product handcrafted cotton with wood and aluminium hardware.
Very compact and you can take it everywhere. You can use it both inside and outside.
We suggest to buy a Baby Safety Harness to prevent your child from falling out.
QUALITY
We ensure high quality of work processes to made each Baby Swing Chair:
- We use 2 pounds (1 kg) of cotton for each chair, that's why the whole chair weight 3,5 pounds (1,6 kg)
- The cotton threads are made of 30 cotton wires each one and very well twisted together.
- Rounded edges
- Handmade carton box to well protect the swing chair and avoid mildew. This is also a more ecological than plastic.
MATERIALS
100% cotton. Wood bars rounded edges.
The seat is cotton handwoven (see the image detail)
Handmade pillow on request (see the options)
For custom color, please write me.
MORE INFO
Fill your babies life with colorful smiles enjoying this Baby Swing Chair made in Nicaragua, with over 100 years traditional design. The baby swing can be used both indoor and outdoor; on the patio or in the garden under the shadow on a tree. Hang the Baby Swing Chair in a safe location and appropriate high best suited for your baby. 
Always hang from a secure beam or support! 
Babies should never be left unattended!
We suggest to buy a Baby Safety Harness to prevent your child from falling out.
Please use responsibly, we are not responsible for any possible injuries incurred while using this product.
About the hanging points, with one hanging point the baby can swing back and forth and spin (like this: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cz-TAQu7QKs) , with two hanging points she/he can only swing only back and forth. 
SPECS & CARE
Baby age: from 5 months to any age under the weight limit / sitting area: 10'' x 10''
Weight limit: 100 lbs (45 kg)
Materials: Cotton and Madero Negro (Gliricidia sepium)
Thread Thickness: 33 wires (Very Durable)
Height: 10 '' (26 cm)
Length:  14'' (35 cm)
Width: 14'' (35 cm)
Total height from the ceiling: 110 cm
-One hanging point (two on request)
-Rope and mounting hardware not included.
-Store indoors during rain and when not in use, to avoid mildew and preserve its beauty.
-Spot clean.
Package measurements and weight
Height: 15 ⅓ " (39 cm)
Length: 15 " (38 cm)
Width:  4 ¾ " (12 cm)
Weight: 3,5 lbs (1,6 kg)

Product name: Made in the USA - iPad Pro Sleeve with Apple Pencil Pocket - Charcoal Felt for 9.7" iPad Pro, 12.9" iPad Pro or iPad Air, Made in the USA
Description:
Find this same sleeve in Grey (lighter) here: 
www.etsy.com/listing/273888758
A new design for the iPad Pro with Apple Pencil users in mind. Now available for the new 9.7" iPad Pro and the 12.9" iPad Pro. 
:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
TEN NOTES ABOUT THIS NEW DESIGN::
ONE:  Made of 100% Wool felted in Germany. This is the good stuff. We choose this felt specifically over the other German felts as it has a smoother, tighter surface and higher density which makes for more solid stitching. Two full body pieces plus a third that forms the pocket on the front... that's 9mm of felt to protect your goods. Our felt is hand selected for us to ensure we are supplied a consistent color & texture.
TWO:  Our stitching is heavy-duty bonded nylon by American & Effird and we are very specific about stitch length, placement and reinforcement. The reinforced 'starts and stops' (referred to as backtacking) and carefully designed corner details carry throughout our line. We keep the space between the stitches and edge of the felt tight to further minimize profile and create a cleaner look that will maintain with use.
THREE: We've been building felt sleeves since before there was an iPad and our goal has always been to provide sleeves that fit. As the devices have evolved with the additions of Smart Covers, Smart Keyboards, Silicone Cases we've opened up our sizing to accommodate. Beyond looking at sizes, we also pay attention to materiality of these accessories and how that affects your use of the sleeve. Those sleeves sized to accommodate Smart Covers/Keyboards and/or Silicone Cases are slightly oversized to allow for those items to slide in and out easily but sized still close enough to feel tailored and that your device is secure. See HOW TO CHOOSE YOUR SIZE below for the different sizes available. 
FOUR: Need more security that just a perfect fit? We get it. We love this sleeve and feel comfortable with the open end but if you really want it, we can add leather strap to the opening similar to our other designs. Cost is an extra 20 and you can choose between brown or black leather we cut from hides we have custom finished for us by Wickett & Craig Tannery in Pennsylvania. Contact us to set-up a custom order. Adding a strap is suggested for those users who plan to purchase sleeves to accommodate covers or cases but also want the flexibility of sometimes leaving those covers off. The strap will keep everything in place regardless of contents.
FIVE: Let's talk about the Apple Pencil pocket. This pocket structure was designed with Apple Pencil users in mind. First, the width of the Apple Pencil pocket is designed to allow you to reach in with your thumb and forefinger to grab the Pencil. If you been using the Apple Pencil, you know that the end of the Pencil comes off easily so you need to be able reach deeper, beyond the end to pull it out. The slanted pocket design is intentional as it gives you variable depth and the ability to choose how low you tuck your Pencil if you want it fully concealed below the lip of the pocket.
SIX:  The second pocket offers a little extra storage best suited for flat/thin items: cords, earbuds, notebooks. On the 9.7" iPad Pro, this pocket is about 4.5" wide. On the 12.9" iPad Pro, this pocket is 6.5" wide or more and some 12.9" users have found they can use this pocket to tuck in their thin, wireless keyboards such as Logitech's Keys-To-Go.  This pocket will not fit Apple's Magic Keyboard but if you want a sleeve for that, we have one coming soon. For your reference, the notebook shown in this pocket is a standard size FEILD NOTES notebook.
SEVEN: Need a spot for your iPad Pro charger? Check out our Small Storage Accessories. The Small Dumpling is perfect for your iPad Pro charger: 
www.etsy.com/listing/267155414/wooly-dumplings
EIGHT:  Every byrd & belle product is made in small batches (and sometimes one at a time) in our studio in Minneapolis, Minnesota. You can find more information on who makes your items and see photos of where they are made: 
https://www.etsy.com/shop/byrdandbelle/about
NINE:  Our studio maintains a low-impact initiative where we balance the quality of our materials with our environmental impact. We choose felt as our main material because beyond its beauty and its addictive texture, it is a rapidly renewable resource, fully biodegradable, LEED recognized and Oeko-Tex certified. Choosing to have your device case made out of felt rather than other materials such as canvas means you've chosen a natural material that acts as exterior material, interior lining and padding in one, eliminating multiple sourcing routes and petroleum-based foam. Our only wish is that someone in the USA would manufacture this material but for now, we'll stick with the Germans as they have a higher level of workplace standards & equality than other countries we've seen supplying felt. It costs a little more. It's worth it.
TEN:  We want your experience with our studio to be a good one. Beyond our return policy, we are here over the life span of this item. The need for repairs is rare, but we make them and usually for free. If you upgrade to a thinner/smaller device, we might be able to modify your sleeve/case to suit or make it into something else entirely. Our materials are chosen to last and often times outlast your device. Let's figure out a way to keep it in use. 
Whoa. Thanks for reading... you deserve a prize. Here's a discount code for 15% off: FIFTEENOFFPRO
:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
HOW TO CHOOSE YOUR SIZE::
Available for the new 9.7" iPad Pro, 12.9" iPad Pro and the iPad Air. We've made extended sizes available for those users using Apple's Smart Covers, Smart Keyboards and/or Silicone Cases on their devices. Choose your iPad and tell us which Apple Accessories you are using in the pulldown menus so we can size your sleeve correctly:
CHOOSE YOUR IPAD:
- iPad Pro (9.7")
- iPad Pro (12.9")
- iPad Air 1/2
ACCESSORIES YOU USE ON YOUR IPAD?:
- None / Naked (you have nothing on your iPad)
- Smart Cover/Smart Keyboard (by Apple, attaches via magnetic hinge and covers the front)
- Silicone Case (by Apple, snaps the back, covers the back & sides)
- Both (You are using both a Smart Cover or Smart Keyboard on the front and a Silicone Case on the back)
**All covers and cases referenced are manufactured by Apple. If you don't know what you have, visit the Apple website. Any third-party covers/cases may require custom orders. Contact us to inquire.
:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::

Product name: Silk Scarf, Mothers Day Gift, Wings Scarf, Spring Summer Scarf, Digital Print Sarong, Hand Painted Feather Shawl, Girlfriend Gift, Silk Wrap
Description:
This unique bohemian wings and bird feathers shawl scarf features:
Delicately hand-painted and digitally printed Art of Wide-Spread Wings, this highly detailed representation of Nature, Freedom and Beauty is my Labor of Love. Just put it over your shoulders to look & feel divine. This scarf would make the most amazing gift for your loved ones!
Truly versatile, this scarf looks great paired with any outfit, SO many ways to wear it! Classic scarf or shawl, tube top or halter top, as a bandana or turban, sarong or wrap skirt... this piece of Art will protect you from Sun and will add that special something to any outfit. 
❂ FABRICS
- Cotton: 100% cotton - sheer matte light material, breathes and drapes well
- Silk/cotton: 50% silk, 50% cotton as seen on the photos - delicate, silky, super soft texture, flows beautifully, has a tad of sheen to it, true black
- 100% Silk satin: High-end, Luxurious, soft, delicate, super soft texture, flows beautifully, has a tad of sheen to it
Please note that my scarves are Fashion scarves, they are NOT meant to keep you warm, unless it's a Cashmere version.
❂ COLOR/PRINT
Beautiful Fresh shades of color - they are both subdued, powerful and otherworldly. You can see every stroke and watercolor hues... Enjoy Vintage Greens, Creams with hints of Yellow and Browns.
Scarf print is one sided, the opposite side is just a little paler.
***Colors might vary slightly from print to print and from your screen***
❂ MEASUREMENTS
When laid flat finished scarf measures approximately: 200 cm by 70 ( 78" X 27") The model in the photos is 5'4, keep that in mind If you are taller.
❂ FINISH
Neat edges, two shortest edges have Fray, gives the scarf a bohemian touch.
❂ CARE
This is a Special piece made from delicate soft material, please treat it accordingly:
If you wish to hand wash, immerse and gently rinse. Never rub or soak. Lay flat to dry in shade. The gentler you are, the longer it will look great. Do not wet (as in rain) before first wash.
❂ SHIPPING
Regular Post (not trackable) is 10 for all International orders and 7 within Australia. 
You can add Tracking (if it applies to your country), Express, Register or Insurance at check out.
To see which countries have a trackable service please look here; 
http://auspost.com.au/parcels-mail/pack-and-track-international.html
Please note that if Pack and Track is not available in your country, it will be shipped with Registered mail which does not offer tracking service.
Shipping charges are paid to the Post office and reflect shipping and handling fees as well as low cost packaging.
❂ RETURN/EXCHANGE
If you don't LOVE it, I'll reimburse or exchange an unworn / unused item. Please contact me if you have any issues or questions.
